text: Linnemann is a German surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Carsten Linnemann (born 1977), German economist *Eduard Linnemann (1841-1886), German chemist *Eta Linnemann (1926-2009), German theologian *Felix Linnemann (1882-1948), German executive *James T.
